@baseUrl = http://localhost:5197
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Create PayOS payment link (requires auth) - NEW canonical route
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payment/payos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "3baa5972-5781-4727-a59d-1e3908e1d1d7",
  "totalAmount": 279999950.00,
  "description": "Thanh toan tien"
}

### [DEPRECATED] Create PayOS payment link via legacy "/create" suffix
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payment/payos/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "3baa5972-5781-4727-a59d-1e3908e1d1d7",
  "totalAmount": 279999950.00,
  "description": "Thanh toan tien"
}

### Generate signed webhook payload (DEV only)
# Copy the response JSON and POST it to /api/v1/payment/payos/webhook
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dev/payos/webhook-simulator/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderCode": 260417034039106,
  "amount": 280000000,
  "status": "PAID",
  "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
  "id": "evt-dev-001"
}

### Post webhook to API (no auth; needs raw body) - NEW canonical route
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/webhooks/payos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "orderCode": 260417034039106,
    "amount": 280000000,
    "status": "PAID",
    "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
    "id": "evt-dev-001"
  },
  "signature": "REPLACE_WITH_SIGNATURE_FROM_GENERATE_CALL"
}

### [DEPRECATED] Post webhook via legacy route
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payment/payos/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "orderCode": 260417034039106,
    "amount": 280000000,
    "status": "PAID",
    "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
    "id": "evt-dev-001"
  },
  "signature": "REPLACE_WITH_SIGNATURE_FROM_GENERATE_CALL"
}

### Trigger webhook end-to-end (DEV only) - one-step: pass flat fields, backend signs & runs webhook pipeline
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/dev/payos/webhook-simulator/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderCode": 260417034039106,
  "amount": 280000000,
  "status": "PAID",
  "paymentLinkId": "8ed4922ccc074d579e97dfae1a3f08d3",
  "id": "evt-dev-trigger-001"
}

@HostAddress = http://localhost:5197
@JwtToken = replace_with_returned_token

### TẠO USER MỚI (REGISTER)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "SecurePassword123!"
}

###

### ĐĂNG NHẬP VÀ LẤY TOKEN (LOGIN) -- TÀI KHOẢN ADMIN CHUẨN ĐƯỢC SEEDING SẴN
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@mebisoft.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### ĐỔI MỚI TOKEN (REFRESH TOKEN) -- Thay AccessToken và RefreshToken thực tế vào đây
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR...",
  "refreshToken": "chuỗi_refresh_token_ngẫu_nhiên"
}

### TEST GÓC NHÌN BẢO MẬT ROLE ADMIN - NEW (chỉ bật trong Development)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/dev/sanity/admin-profile
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### [DEPRECATED] Legacy auth/admin-profile
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/admin-profile
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Add item to cart - NEW RESTful
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "quantity": 1
}

### [DEPRECATED] Add item via /cart/add
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cart/add
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Checkout cart (optionally select subset via cartItemIds)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cart/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": 1,
  "shipping": null,
  "cartItemIds": null
}

### [DEPRECATED] Checkout selected items (use /cart/checkout with cartItemIds)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/cart/checkout-selected
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentMethod": 1,
  "cartItemIds": [],
  "shipping": null
}

### Create shipment for order - NEW
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/shipment
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "SGN-BIKE"
}

### [DEPRECATED] Create shipment via /create-shipment
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/create-shipment
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "SGN-BIKE"
}

### Post review for a product - NEW nested
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great!"
}

### [DEPRECATED] Post review via /reviews
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Great!"
}

### Admin create product - NEW
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample",
  "price": 100000,
  "sku": "SKU-DEMO",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### [DEPRECATED] Admin create via /products
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/products
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample",
  "price": 100000,
  "sku": "SKU-DEMO",
  "categoryId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Huỷ đơn hàng (owner, trạng thái Pending/Confirmed & chưa thanh toán)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - liệt kê đơn hàng (filter status, khoảng ngày, paging)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/orders?status=0&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - chi tiết đơn hàng theo ID
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - liệt kê coupon
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/coupons?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - chi tiết coupon
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/coupons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - liệt kê promotion
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/promotions?isActive=true&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - chi tiết promotion
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/promotions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - liệt kê variant theo productId
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/variants?productId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

### Admin - chi tiết variant
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/admin/variants/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{JwtToken}}

###
